wiki.summary: On “private island,” the opening track ”DS4EVER”, Gunna talks about his rough upbringing, expressing his comeuppance. The song features a melodic guitar-trap beat produced by Wheezy, similar to “ARGENTINA,” the intro to Gunna’s last album, ”WUNNA”. When the song leaked in December 2021, there was a rumor going around that Kanye West was involved with the production of this song, but the rumor was debunked as false. “private island” debuted at #68 on the Billboard Hot 100 week ending January 22, 2022. Read more on Last.fm.
